      "question": "A large multinational corporation is implementing a fraud risk assessment process. The fraud examination team is evaluating which methodology to use for identifying and prioritizing fraud risks across various business units. Which of the following approaches would be MOST effective for conducting a comprehensive fraud risk assessment?",
