      "question": "A multinational manufacturing company is implementing a fraud risk management program and wants to leverage data analytics to detect potential fraudulent activities in its procurement process. The company processes over 50,000 purchase orders annually across multiple subsidiaries. Which of the following data analytics techniques would be MOST effective in identifying anomalous patterns indicative of procurement fraud?",
